REPORT Z_ABPTRAIN_SML_EXER16.

*Exercise 16 - Maintain Selection Text

*Parameter Declaration
PARAMETERS: p_empNum(6) TYPE n,
            p_fName TYPE string,
            p_lName TYPE string,
            p_bdate TYPE d,
            p_salary TYPE string,
            p_hobby TYPE string.

*Display input
WRITE: |Employee Number: { p_empNum }|,
     / |Full Name: { p_fName } { p_lName }|,
     / |Birthdate: { p_bdate }|,
     / |Dream Salary: { p_salary }|,
     / |Hobby: { p_hobby }|.
